UID:TU1953318997
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Intro to NW Indiana take 2 - Prettier\, less grittier and John Dill
 inger (Len Krietz)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Moderate\n\nDistance: 41 miles\n\nLe
 ader: Len Krietz\n\n## Intro to NW Indiana Take 2 - Prettier\, less gritti
 er\, and John Dillinger\n\nAnother foray into Northwest Indiana. Starting 
 in downtown Highland\, Indiana\, the ride will travel from Highland to Cro
 wn Point and back\, mainly on trails. In downtown Crown Point we'll pass b
 y the "escape proof" Old Lake County Jail from which John Dillinger escape
 d\, and have lunch/brunch at One 13 North Kitchen and Bar. We'll ride on p
 arts of the Erie Lackawana Trail\, CO Greenway\, Oak Savana Trai\, and Pen
 nsey Greenway.\n\nDistance: 41 miles\n\nPace: Moderate (13-15 mph)\n\nStar
 t Time : 9am\n\nREMOTE STARTt: Erie Lackawanna Trail Head \, Highland IN -
  Downton Highland Parking Lot on the corner of Highway Ave and Kennedy ave
 \n\nhttps://ridewithgps.com/routes/52260390\n\nQuestions? Contact : Len Kr
 ietz at lkrietz2@gmail.com\n\n
LOCATION:Downtown Highland parking lot\nHighland\, IN 46322
CATEGORIES:..Moderate (13-15 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
