 dge.jpg This week's Thursday Casual ride: we will take off eastbound from 
 Chandler to the lakefront\, then south into Chicago. From Rogers Ave. we'l
 l go south on the bike route west of Sheridan Road\, mostly Greenview Ave.
  At Berwyn Ave. we'll head west and later south to pick up the trail along
  the North Branch of the Chicago River\, including the Riverview Bridge. A
 t Belmont we'll turn around to head back north\, along the River and then 
 the canal along McCormick. Lunch will be in Ravenswood Manor or Ravenswood
 . We will discuss places to eat Thursday before departure.\n\n
