 ct" – Grant and Gross Point Rd\, Skokie. 7 miles- Casual Pace (10-12mph)
 .\n\nThis ride will meander through the neighborhoods\, parks and trails i
 n Skokie and Northwest Evanston. We will ride through neighborhoods to che
 ck out fall colors right in our own back yards. The route will feature two
