UID:TU1976397948
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Corned Beef\, Latkes and Hot Fudge Sundaes on Sunday (Alvin Spector
 )
DESCRIPTION:Status: CANCELLED!\n\nPace: Fast\n\nDistance: ~ 40 Miles\n\nLea
 der: Alvin Spector\n\n## !https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Corned%20Beef%20
 Sandwich.jpgCorned Beef\, Latkes and Hot Fudge Sundaes on a Sunday\n\n!htt
 ps://ebcrides.org/images/cal/RWGPS-route.png: https://ridewithgps.com/rout
 es/46435755Please come on out for a classic Fast (15-17 mph) ride to the f
 amous Manny’s Deli just off Roosevelt Road and Jefferson south of the Lo
 op. A favorite of Chicago politicians as well as the general public\, Mann
 y’s is an institution of deli delights including one of the best corned 
 beef sandwiches and potato pancakes\, anywhere. Founded in 1942\, this is 
 a family run institution where everything\, including the corned beef is h
 omemade. After lunch\, we will ride to Margie’s Candies on Western Avenu
 e. A Chicago landmark for over a century\, this old fashioned candy store 
 and ice cream parlor will provide the perfect dessert for the ride back to
  Wilmette. Total distance approximately 40 miles.\n\n
LOCATION:Panera\, Wilmette
CATEGORIES:.Fast (15-17 mph)
