BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU1957592116
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Club Meeting: NSC Recap and Grant Recipient Presentations (Anne Gla
 ser)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nLeader: Anne Glaser\n\nZOOM program begins
  at 7:00 PM\n\nEvanston Bike Club October Meeting is at 7:00 pm via Zoom. 
 In addition to the board elections and a recap of the North Shore Century 
 (NSC)\, there will be presentations from EBC grant recipients. Attendees w
 ill learn how some of the recipients of this year’s EBC grants program a
 re using the funds raised at the North Shore Century on bike-related proje
 cts and activities to make a difference in their communities.\n\n
