SUMMARY:Weds Very Fast Plus Ride to Lake Bluff (John McBlain)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Very Fast Plus\n\nDistance: 43 miles
 \n\nLeader: John McBlain\n\n# \\*\\*Very Fast Plus Loop to Lake Bluff\n\nV
 ery Fast Plus group will ride about 43 miles with a snack stop in Lake Blu
 ff. Many stretches are self-paced with a paceline for part of the ride. On
  the Skokie Valley Trail northbound the speeds pick up and the group somet
 imes splits into two or more groups. Southbound the group may also split a
 fter it reaches Green Bay Road. The mixture of Fast Plus and Very Fast Plu
 s speeds makes this an ideal ride for Fast Plus riders who want to challen
 ge themselves. Ride Leader: John McBlain jlmcblain@comcast.net\n\n
LOCATION:Centennial Park Ice Rink\, Wilmette
CATEGORIES:.Weekly > Very Fast Plus Wkly
