BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU1975826865
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Club Meeting:  Staying Fit During the Winter by Cross-Country Skiin
 g (Anne Glaser)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nLeader: Anne Glaser\n\n## Club meeting: **
 Staying Fit During the Winter by Cross-Country Skiing**\n\n## Refreshments
  at 7pm\, program begins at 7:30pm\n\nTim Weaver\, VP of Northwest Nordic 
 Ski Club (NNSC)\, and Scott Schaedel\, NNSC Treasurer and Website manager\
 , will discuss the basics and common myths about cross-country skiing. A "
 count the EBC members in NNSC photos contest" will award a fabulous prize 
 to those nearest to the correct number. An entertaining short video will c
 aution would-be cross-country skiers to the dangers of becoming too involv
 ed in this sport. NNSC hosts various activities throughout the year includ
 ing snowshoeing\, local hikes\, trips\, dinner meetings\, kayaking\, pickl
 eball\, and fun social activities in the north and northwest suburbs.\n\nT
 he in-person meeting at the Robert Crown Center (1801 Main St\, Evanston) 
 will begin at 7:30 pm with club business followed by the program starting 
 around 7:50 pm. Refreshments will be available starting at 7 pm.\n\n
LOCATION:Robert Crown Center\, Multipurpose Room B\, 1801 Main Street\, Eva
 nston\, IL
CATEGORIES:_Meetings/Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20251118T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20251118T210000
