DESCRIPTION:Status: CANCELLED!\n\nPace: Casual\n\nDistance: 7 miles\n\nLead
 er: David Barish\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Christmas%20Lights%20
 Displays.jpgThe Skokie Bike Network has revived the old EBC Holiday Lights
  Ride.\n\nThe ride leaves at 4pm from Sketchbook Brewery and Taproom \, 49
 01 Main St.\, Skokie: https://www.sketchbookbrewing.com/skokie. We will ta
 ke the Valley Line trail to Pratt and then to Longmeadow and the neighborh
 ood where all the light displays will be. It is a short ride of just a few
  miles but the lights are much better from a bike than from a car. When we
  get back to Sketchbook we can debate which display was the best over a lo
 cal beverage. Come join us!\n\nhttps://skokiebikenet.org/\n\n
