BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU1765500814
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Club Meeting: Annual Holiday Pot Luck (Evanston Bicycle Club)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nLeader: Evanston Bicycle Club\n\n!https://
 ebcrides.org/images/cal/Holiday%20Potluck.jpg Annual Holiday Potluck: Dece
 mber 17\n\nThe annual Holiday Potluck will be held on Tuesday\, December 1
 7 at 6:30 pm at Robert Crown Center (1801 Main St\, Evanston) in Multipurp
 ose Rooms A\, B\, and C (immediately upon entering Robert Crown\, turn lef
 t down a small hallway to the Multipurpose Rooms).\n\nAll EBC members and 
 a plus 1 are invited to the dinner. Please bring a dish to share with a ut
 ensil for serving. We'll have power strips and extension cords for anyone 
 bringing a hot dish. Label your container and utensil and include a brief 
 description of your dish to assist those who may have any food sensitivi-t
 y. Plates\, utensils\, napkins\, cups\, and beverages will be provided. Th
 e food will be set up in Multipurpose A while Multipurpose B/C will have t
 ables set up for dining.\n\nIf you would like to assist with setting up th
 e potluck or have any questions\, contact Joan Welch at jwelch4252@gmail.c
 om or (843)729-0705. See you at 6:30 pm\, Tuesday\, December 17 at Robert 
 Crown!\n\n
LOCATION:Robert Crown Center\, Multipurpose Room B\, 1801 Main Street\, Eva
 nston\, IL
CATEGORIES:_Meetings/Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
