SUMMARY:Club Meeting: Ride Illinois (Anne Glaser)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nLeader: Anne Glaser\n\n**January 20 – Ri
 de Illinois**\n\nThe Executive Director of Ride Illinois\, Dave Simmons\, 
 will provide updates on their advocacy work\, legislative priorities movin
 g forward in 2026\, education\, and awareness efforts. Ride Illinois is a 
 nonprofit organization dedicated to making biking better throughout the st
 ate. They are an advocate for all Illinois bicyclists\, promoting bicycle 
 access\, education\, and safety.\n\nThe in-person meeting at the Robert Cr
 own Center (1801 Main St\, Evanston) will begin at 7:30 pm with club busin
 ess followed immediately by the program. Refreshments will be available st
 arting at 7 pm.\n\n
