UID:TU1601334731
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Club Meeting: Winter Dinner ($) (Evanston Bicycle Club)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nLeader: Evanston Bicycle Club\n\nThe EBC w
 inter dinner returns February 4\, 2024\, at The Lawn\, the restaurant at t
 he Wilmette Golf Club\, 3900 Fairway Dr.\, Wilmette. Cash bar and appetize
 rs will start at 6 p.m. with dinner following at 7 p.m. We will celebrate 
 another year of biking and friendship\, honor those who contributed to EBC
 ’s success in 2023 and recognize the Club members who led and participat
 ed on rides. Registration is required and will open later this month with 
 more details and menu choices available then. The subsidized price is $20 
 per person with the balance of the cost underwritten by the EBC.\n\nRequir
 ed registration will open in January with more details and menu choices av
 ailable then. The price per person will remain at $20\, with the balance o
 f the cost underwriten by EBC.\n\nIf you would like to assist with plannin
 g the dinner or help out at the dinner\, contact Doug Hoffman\, EBC presid
 ent\, at president@ebc.org or Helen Oloroso at hlnoloroso@gmail.com.\n\n
LOCATION:The Wilmette Golf Club
CATEGORIES:_Meetings/Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
