UID:TU2051901888
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Tour of the Mississippi River Valley (TOMRV) (Scott Schaedel)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Fast\, Any\n\nDistance: approx 140 m
 iles\n\nLeader: Scott Schaedel\n\n# !https://www.ebcrides.org/browser/uplo
 ad/TOMRV.jpgTour Of the Mississippi River Valley (TOMRV)\n\nTOMRV_2026: ht
 tps://qcbc.org/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=505193&module_id=324415 wil
 l start from Goose Lake\, IA on June 6 with an overnight and return on Jun
 e 7. The route is approximately 70 miles on both days\; optional start in 
 Bettendorf\, IA for approximately 100 miles each day. Click on the link ab
 ove for registration information. RSVP to Scott Schaedel (svschaed2@gmail.
 com) so that I can add you to a texting list for meeting logistics. Lodgin
 g is suggested at a hotel in Clinton\, IA for Friday night before the ride
  start on Saturday. Clinton is about a 30 minute drive to the start of the
  ride. The ride features scenic views of the river valley and supported re
 st stops as well as baggage transport to the Saturday overnight in DuBuque
 \, IA. TOMRV offers hotel information in Bettendorf\, but early riders can
  reserve dormitory room sleeping space at Loras College. Saturday dinner a
 t the college is also included.\n\nRegister at: TOMRV_2026: https://qcbc.o
 rg/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=505193&module_id=324415\n\n
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:TRUE
CATEGORIES:...Any,.Fast (15-17 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
