BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU2025835100
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:First Draft Grayslake (Will Heelan)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Fast\n\nDistance: 54 Miles\n\nLeader
 : Will Heelan\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/RWGPS-route.png!https://
 ebcrides.org/images/cal/First%20Draft%20Grayslake.jpg: https://ridewithgps
 .com/routes/39835533The route starts at the Village green in Northbrook. I
 t goes up through Libertyville to Gray's Lake where we have lunch at First
  Draft Grayslake. It returns through scenic Independence Grove FP in Liber
