UID:TU1981580481
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Club Meeting: Annual Holiday Pot Luck (Evanston Bicycle Club)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nLeader: Evanston Bicycle Club\n\n!https://
 ebcrides.org/images/cal/Holiday%20Potluck.jpg The annual Holiday Potluck w
 ill be held on Tuesday\,  \nDecember 16 at 6:30 pm at Robert Crown Center 
  \n(1801 Main St\, Evanston) in Multipurpose Rooms A\,  \nB\, and C (immed
 iately upon entering Robert Crown\,  \nturn left to the Multipurpose Rooms
 ). This will be a zero-waste event with on-site composting. All EBC member
 s are invited to the dinner. Please bring a dish to share with a utensil f
 or serving. Due to limited space\, we will not have any accommodations for
  plugging in crockpots or heating trays. Label your container and utensil 
 and include a brief description of your dish to assist those who may have 
 any food sensitivity. Plates\, utensils\, napkins\, cups\, and beverages w
 ill be provided. The food will be set up in Multipurpose A while Multipurp
 ose B/C will have tables set up for dining. If you would like to assist wi
 th setting up the potluck or have any questions\, contact Joan Welch at jw
 elch4252@gmail.com or (843) 729-0705. See you at 6:30 pm\, Tuesday\, Decem
 ber 16 at Robert Crown!\n\n
LOCATION:Robert Crown Center\, Multipurpose Room B\, 1801 Main Street\, Eva
 nston\, IL
CATEGORIES:_Meetings/Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
