 wp-content/uploads/2012/03/easter-basket.jpg**LEAVING PANERA @ 09:00 AM**.
  Join us at 9:00 am on Easter Sunday for a Moderate ride (13-15mph) to Lak
 e Forest College for brunch. If the Easter Brunch Fast Ride is too fast fo
 r you\, but you still want to enjoy the abundant brunch (for only $12.50) 
 join us at Panera in Wilmette @ 9am for the Moderate version! Note: The ri
 de will not happen if it is raining\, snowing or otherwise miserable out. 
  \nDon't eat breakfast before you leave for this ride! This ride is back b
 y popular demand after being on hiatus since 2019. For those of you who th
 ink inflation is now running rampant\, **check this out**: Fabulous brunch
  (Lake Forest College students eat very\, very well) - this year for a spe
 cial deal of only **$12.50** (cash or credit card). (FYI: **2019**-$16.00\
 ; **2018**-$11.35\; **2017**-$10.31\; **2016**-9.92\; **2015**-$9.55)\n\n
