 ttps://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Happy%20New%20Year%202026.jpg **Roll in the
  New Year on the bike!**\n\nRide from Panera down to the Lincoln Park Cons
 ervatory\, then a lunch stop at nearby Nookies on Wells. DRESS WARM AND BR
 ING A GOOD LOCK! This year\, the Lincoln Park Conservatory turns cozy with
  its “Fireside” Winter Flower Show. A centerpiece brick fireplace radi
 ates relaxation\, while featured poinsettia varieties such as ‘Golden Gl
 o’\, ‘Norwin Orange’ and ‘Christmas Magic Red’ capture the color
 s of a comforting fire. Fresh cut fir trees are a soothing scent\, as ambe
 r lighting creates a soft glow.. Ride leader will make reservations as nee
 ded.\n\nRoute from my library. https://ridewithgps.com/routes/49340944\n\n
