UID:TU1802216664
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Wilmette Fireworks Dinner Ride (Will Heelan)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Moderate\n\nDistance: 25 Miles\n\nLe
 ader: Will Heelan\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Fireworks.jpg!https:
 //ebcrides.org/images/cal/RWGPS-route.png: https://ridewithgps.com/routes/
 43548306EBC Fireworks Enthusiasts: Wilmette will hold its annual Independe
 nce Day Fireworks Display on July 3rd at 9:30pm at the lakefront in Gillso
 n Park and we are planning to be there! This moderate ride will **start at
  Panera Wilmette at 6 pm** to take a 20 mile scenic loop north\, returning
  to Panera in Wilmette around 8 pm. After picking up our carry-out dinners
  we will proceed to the eastern lawn of the Baha'i Temple (just off the we
 st public sidewalk on Sheridan Road south of the Wilmette Harbor bridge an
 d about 90 feet north of Linden Avenue). There we will stake out our viewi
 ng location and enjoy our picnic while we wait for the fireworks to start.
  Feel free to join us for any or all of these activities. This ride is a g
 reat way to celebrate the Independence Day holiday! **Lights and helmets m
 andatory**\, something to sit on highly recommended\, (also consider bug r
 epellant if you are susceptible).\n\n
LOCATION:Panera Wilmette
CATEGORIES:..Moderate (13-15 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
