BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU1802216707
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Horsey Hundred (Timothy Weaver)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Fast\, Any\n\nDistance: 26 to 103 mi
 les\n\nLeader: Timothy Weaver\n\n# !https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Horsey
 %20Hundred.jpgThe Horsey Hundred\n\n**May 22-24\, 2026**\n\nRegister: http
 s://www.bikereg.com/horsey-hundred\n\nFees: $95 early bird (by 3.31.2026)\
 ; $110 by 5.9.2026\n\nThe Horsey Hundred is the premier cycling event in K
 entucky and the signature event of the Bluegrass Cycling Club\, Lexington.
  Since 1978 the HH has grown to hosting up to 2500 riders.\n\nThe weekend 
 begins with fun and festivities on Friday\, featuring optional rides in Bl
 uegrass country\, numerous cycling-related vendors\, food trucks\, and ent
 ertainment.\n\nSaturday is the flagship ride with 6 route choices\, rangin
 g from 27 miles to the iconic century (102 miles). On Sunday you have your
  choice of 3 rides\, ranging from 31 to 63 miles. On both days you will wi
 nd your way though some of the most beautiful scenery you can imagine\, in
 cluding horse farms\, stone fences\, rivers\, streams\, lush pastures\, hi
 storic towns\, and bourbon distilleries.\n\nThe ride is fully supported wi
 th frequent rest stops featuring delicious\, nutritional food chosen to fu
 el your journey.\n\nTim Weaver will lead a Fast (15-17 mph) ride on Saturd
 ay\, but participants may ride whatever pace and distance they choose.\n\n
 **RSVP via email is appreciated**: tawpretzel@gmail.com\n\nFor complete in
 formation: https://horseyhundred.com/\n\na) Pace: Any\n\nb) Date\, startin
 g location: **May 22-24\, 2026\, Charles Brooking Park\, Georgetown\, KY\n
 \nc) Distance: your choice\n\nd) Ride leader’s name and email address: T
 im Weaver: tawpretzel@gmail.com\n\ne ) RSVP via email appreciated: tawpret
 zel@gmail.com\n\n
LOCATION:Charles Brooking Park\, Georgetown\, KY 40324
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:TRUE
CATEGORIES:...Any,.Fast (15-17 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260522
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260525
CREATED:20250104T044436Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T183655Z
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=5;BYDAY=4FR
X-TEAMUP-STATUS:Confirmed
X-TEAMUP-PACE:Fast\, Any
X-TEAMUP-DISTANCE:26 to 103 miles
X-TEAMUP-START-LOCATION:Charles Brooking Park\, Georgetown\, KY 40324
X-TEAMUP-LEADER:Timothy Weaver
END:VEVENT
