 pen in January with more details and menu choices available then. The pric
 e per person will remain at $20\, with the balance of the cost underwriten
  by EBC.\n\nIf you would like to assist with planning the dinner or help o
 ut at the dinner\, contact Margaret Stender at president@ebc.org or Helen 
 Oloroso at hlnoloroso@gmail.com.\n\n
