BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU2023025248
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Gus's Drive-In\, Wisconsin (Neal Ney)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Moderate\n\nDistance: 49 Miles\n\nLe
 ader: Neal Ney\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/RWGPS-route.png: https:
 //ridewithgps.com/routes/30880656\n\n!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/guss
 -drive-in-east-troy.jpgI love to ride in the SE Wisconsin countryside near
  Burlington\, and Gus’s Drive-in is a favorite lunch spot. We have had f
 ast and fast plus paced rides in this area for years. A few years back Ken
  Schulein put together a shorter route suitable for moderate riders that h
 as become one of my favorite routes in this area. The route travels on rur
 al roads with rolling hills to Gus's Drive-in\, East Troy\, WI for lunch a
 t mile 25. Rest Stops with snacks are at mile 12 and Adrian's Frozen Custa
 rd in Burlington at mile 38.\n\nWisconsin Start: Brighton_Dale_Golf_Course
 : https://www.google.com/maps/place/Brighton+Dale+Links/@42.6305121%20-88.
 1179985%2012z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x8805790ac45286f9:0x24038a6eaef072f2. Take 
 I-94 North. 7.5 miles past the Wisconsin border take Exit #340 WI-142 West
  toward Burlington. Turn left (west) at the end of the exit ramp and go we
 st 8.5 miles on WI-142. Turn right (north) at WI-75 (248th St) and go 0.7 
 miles. Turn left into golf course entrance. Follow the park road about 0.5
  mile to the parking lot next to the club house. Park at an empty area of 
 the lot. Allow an hour and 15 minutes from Evanston.\n\n
LOCATION:Brighton Dale Golf Course\, WI
CATEGORIES:..Moderate (13-15 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260822T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260822T090000
CREATED:20260112T230618Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260301T200655Z
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=8;BYDAY=4SA
X-TEAMUP-STATUS:Confirmed
X-TEAMUP-PACE:Moderate
X-TEAMUP-DISTANCE:49 Miles
X-TEAMUP-START-LOCATION:Brighton Dale Golf Course\, WI
X-TEAMUP-LEADER:Neal Ney
END:VEVENT
