BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU2023025284
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:Western Suburbs Meander\, Fall Edition (Rebecca Tung)
DESCRIPTION:Status: CHANGES PENDING!\n\nPace: Moderate\n\nDistance: 46 mile
 s\n\nLeader: Rebecca Tung\n\n# !https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Southern%2
 0Caf%C3%A9.jpg\n\n# !https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Madison%20Meadow%20Lo
 mbard.jpg\n\n## Western Suburbs Meander\, Fall Edition\n\nRemote start at 
 Madison Meadows Park in Lombard at 9AM\, Madison St entrance (Madison &amp
 \; Chase). We’ll ride at a moderate pace (13-15mph)\, going through Lomb
 ard\, Glen Ellyn\, Wheaton\, Winfield\, West Chicago\, Barlett\, Wayne to 
 St Charles. Lunch at Southern Cafe in St Charles and going back the same w
 ay with minor variations.\n\nThe total riding distance will be 46 miles\, 
 all on-road with some moderately challenging hills. We’ll wait to regrou
 p after the climbs and no one will be left behind. Madison Meadows Park is
  about 70 min from Evanston by car\, it’s approximately 2 miles away fro
 m the Metra station in Lombard. Click this link for exact location https:/
 /maps.app.goo.gl/t6yM2E58HeLYza4Y6\n\n
LOCATION:Madison Meadow Park\, E Madison St & S Ahrens Ave\, Lombard\, IL 6
 0148
CATEGORIES:..Moderate (13-15 mph)
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
