 \, Very Fast\n\n# ***!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/Happy%20New%20Year%2
 02025.jpg***\n\n# ***New Year's Day Show &amp\; Go Rides:***\n\n**The dest
 ination and distance will be decided by the group at the meeting time. Rid
 ers must sign an up-to-date sign-in &amp\; waiver sheet (from EBC website)
  and theremust be at least two people on the ride\, with the leader being 
