 des\, but if no club member is available\, the ride will not be held.**\n\
 n- **Casual Show &amp\; Go Ride (10-12) -**Distance is typically 20 to 30 
 miles with a snack stop. Ride Info: JoG 773.271.5802 jigcsr@gmail.com\n- *
 *Moderate Show &amp\; Go Ride (13-15 mph) -**Distance is typically 30 to 4
 5 miles with a snack stop.Ride Info: DanaT 847.363.6306 danataylor1@comcas
 t.net\n- **Fast Show &amp\; Go Ride (15-17 mph) -**Distance is typically 3
