 0Caf%C3%A9.jpgMeandering through the Western!https://ebcrides.org/images/c
 al/Madison%20Meadow%20Lombard.jpg Suburbs\n\nThis ride will be co-led by R
 ebecca Tung and Rich Rothrock\, who also leads rides with the Elmhurst Bik
 e Club and is very familiar with biking in the western suburbs. It will be
  a remote start from Madison Meadow Park in Lombard\, Madison St entrance 
 (Madison &amp\; Chase). We’ll ride at a moderate pace (13-15mph)\, going
  through Lombard\, Glen Ellyn\, Wheaton\, Winfield\, West Chicago\, Barlet
 t\, Wayne to St Charles.\n\nLunch at the Southern Cafe in St Charles\, hom
 e of the nasty biscuit\, and going back the same way with minor variations
 .\n\nTotal riding distance 46 miles\, all on-road miles. Madison Meadow Pa
 rk is about one hour’s drive from Evanston by car\, approximately 2 mile
 s away from the Metra station in Lombard. Click this link for exact locati
 on: https://maps.app.goo.gl/t6yM2E58HeLYza4Y6\n\n
