UID:TU2055246595
DTSTAMP:20260317T225617Z
SUMMARY:East Dundee (Neal Ney)
DESCRIPTION:Status: Confirmed\n\nPace: Moderate\n\nDistance: 50 miles\n\nLe
 ader: Neal Ney\n\n# **!https://ebcrides.org/images/cal/FoxRiverTrail.jpg!h
 ttps://ebcrides.org/images/cal/RWGPS-route.png: https://ridewithgps.com/ro
 utes/54156920**\n\n# **Moderate 50 miles to East Dundee:**\n\nJoin Neal Ne
 y for a moderate ride starting at the Buffalo Creek Forest Preserve (18163
  Checker Road\, Long Grove\, IL) and going to East Dundee on mostly quiet 
 roads and the scenic Fox River Trail. We'll lunch at *Benedicts_Eggs_and_M
 ore*: https://benedictseggsandmore.com in East Dundee and then return to t
 he Forest Preserve by way of Barrington. There will be some hills on this 
 route\, but we will regather after each climb so no one has to fear being 
 left behind. There is also a long flat section along the scenic Fox River.
  This is a very soul satisfying route.\n\n
LOCATION:Buffalo Creek Forest Preserve\, 18163 Checker Road\, Long Grove\, 
 IL
CATEGORIES:..Moderate (13-15 mph)
